citations:
    citation-agot-prologue:
        source: source-agot
        properties:
            locator: "Prologue"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "POV: Will. Three rangers of the Night's Watch — Ser Waymar Royce, Will, and Gared — encounter the Others beyond the Wall. Royce is killed and reanimates. Will is killed by the reanimated Royce. Gared's subsequent fate is shown in Bran I (he becomes the deserter executed at Winterfell)."
